=== 乌克兰教会争议 ===
2018年4月，巴尔多禄茂宣布正着手整合乌克兰境内名目不一的正教会。同年8月27日，乌克兰总统[[彼得·波罗申科|波罗申科]]宣称巴尔多禄茂已经认可乌克兰教会的自治。31日，巴尔多禄茂与俄罗斯牧首[[基里尔_(莫斯科大牧首)|基里尔]]举行了会晤但没有达成一致。<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-45396464|title=Orthodox Church split fuels Russia-Ukraine tension|author=|date=2018-09-03|work=BBC News|accessdate=2018-09-26|archive-date=2021-01-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210115060815/https://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-45396464|dead-url=no}}</ref>9月，巴尔多禄茂宣布将会承认并给予[[乌克兰正教会_(基辅宗主教圣统)|乌克兰正教会]]自治权，这一动作引起了[[俄罗斯正教会|俄罗斯正教会]]极大的不满。<ref name=":1">{{Cite news|url=https://sputniknews.com/world/201809231068271418-patriarch-constantinople-ukraine-autocephaly/|title=Patriarch of Constantinople Pledges to Grant Autocephaly to Ukraine Church Soon|author=|date=2018-09-23|work=Sputnik|accessdate=2018-09-25|archive-date=2020-11-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201109011927/https://sputniknews.com/world/201809231068271418-patriarch-constantinople-ukraine-autocephaly/|dead-url=no}}</ref>乌克兰议员穆斯塔法·哲米列夫透露，土耳其总统[[雷傑普·塔伊普·艾爾多安|埃尔多安]]在该事件中极力支持巴尔多禄茂，有媒体认为美国政府也在幕后起着作用。<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://moderndiplomacy.eu/2018/09/25/erdogan-andrew-brunson-and-ukrainian-church-autocephaly/|title=Erdogan, Andrew Brunson and Ukrainian Church autocephaly|author=Leyla Yesiltas|date=2018-09-25|work=Modern Diplomacy|accessdate=2018-09-26|archive-date=2020-11-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201124152701/https://moderndiplomacy.eu/2018/09/25/erdogan-andrew-brunson-and-ukrainian-church-autocephaly/|dead-url=no}}</ref>最终，普世牧首区[[厄玛奴耳_(法兰西都主教)|厄玛奴耳]]都主教于10月11日的声明重申了乌克兰教会自治权的授予、普世牧首基辅直辖区的建立、移除乌克兰教会[[菲拉列特·杰尼先科|菲拉列特宗主教]]身上的破门令以及反对“将教会财产佔為己有的行为”。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.patriarchate.org/-/communiq-1|title=Announcement (11/10/2018).|accessdate=2018-10-16|author=Ecumenical Patriarchate|date=2018-10-11|publisher=|archive-date=2018-10-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181011164147/https://www.patriarchate.org/-/communiq-1|dead-url=no}}</ref>11月3日，巴尔多禄茂牧首与乌克兰总统波罗申科签订了一份合作协议，推进其在乌克兰的教会整合计划。<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.kyivpost.com/ukraine-politics/poroshenko-bartholomew-sign-cooperation-agreement-updated.html|title=Poroshenko, Bartholomew sign cooperation agreement (UPDATED)|author=|date=2018-11-04|work=基辅邮报|accessdate=2018-11-04}}</ref>12月15日，普世牧首区宣布建立新的“[[烏克蘭正教會|乌克兰正教会]]”并选举[[伊皮法纽_(基辅都主教)|伊皮法纽]]为新一任的首脑。巴尔多禄茂牧首还邀请伊皮法纽都主教至伊斯坦布尔共同庆祝主显节，届时，牧首会颁布有关乌克兰教会自治的教令。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.patriarchate.org/-/anakoinothen-15-12-2018-?_101_INSTANCE_MF6geT6kmaDE_languageId=en_US|title=Communiqué (15/12/2018)|accessdate=2018-12-20|author=君士坦丁堡普世牧首区|date=2018-12-15|publisher=|archive-date=2019-06-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190609110044/https://www.patriarchate.org/-/anakoinothen-15-12-2018-?_101_INSTANCE_MF6geT6kmaDE_languageId=en_US|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=http://tass.com/society/1036276|title=Schismatic Ukrainian church head to receive autocephaly decree on January 6|author=Mikhail Palinchak|date=2018-12-16|work=塔斯社|accessdate=2018-12-20|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108113222/https://tass.com/society/1036276|dead-url=no}}</ref>1月6日，巴尔多禄茂牧首于[[圣乔治主教座堂|圣乔治座堂]]正式颁布教令授予乌克兰分裂教会自治权。其首脑为伊皮法纽·杜缅科。<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://orthochristian.com/118451.html|title=PATRIARCH BARTHOLOMEW FORMALLY GRANTS TOMOS OF AUTOCEPHALY TO UKRAINIAN SCHISMATIC CHURCH|author=|date=2019-01-06|work=Orthodox Christianity|accessdate=2019-01-08|archive-date=2020-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112034135/https://orthochristian.com/118451.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>对于此教令，[[安条克希腊正教会|安提阿]]牧首[[约翰十世_(安条克希腊正教会)|约翰十世]]<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://orthochristian.com/118455.html|title=“IT IS UNREASONABLE TO STOP A SCHISM AT THE PRICE OF THE UNITY OF THE ORTHODOX WORLD”—PAT. JOHN OF ANTIOCH|author=|date=2019-01-06|work=Orthodox Christianity|accessdate=2019-01-08|archive-date=2020-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112020830/https://orthochristian.com/118455.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>、[[塞爾維亞正教會|塞尔维亚]]牧首[[爱任纽_(塞尔维亚牧首)|爱任纽]]<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://orthochristian.com/118400.html|title=CHAUVINISTS, POLITICIANS, UNIATES, AND CONSTANTINOPLE SPREAD SCHISM IN UKRAINE, SAYS SERBIAN CHURCH (+ VIDEO)|author=|date=2019-01-03|work=Orthodox Christianity|accessdate=2019-01-08|archive-date=2021-02-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210213215417/https://orthochristian.com/118400.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>、全波兰都主教[[萨瓦_(波兰都主教)|萨瓦]]<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://orthochristian.com/118398.html|title=POLISH CHURCH REJECTS PAT. BARTHOLOMEW’S REQUEST TO RECOGNIZE NEW UKRAINIAN CHURCH|author=|date=2019-01-03|work=Orthodox Christianity|accessdate=2019-01-08|archive-date=2021-01-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210107225826/https://orthochristian.com/118398.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>及[[塞浦路斯|塞浦路斯]]大主教屈梭多模<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://orthochristian.com/118512.html?fbclid=IwAR0Hozp5zbExtYQqrH5Qwq4jSIUzXSCF3U-Gt2gOZQLgBabENZ3PlBF7NtI|title=ABP. CHRYSOSTOMOS OF CYPRUS WILL NOT COMMEMORATE HEAD OF UKRAINIAN SCHISMATICS|author=|date=2019-01-09|work=Orthodox Christianity|accessdate=2019-01-10|archive-date=2020-08-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200808001442/http://orthochristian.com/118512.html?fbclid=IwAR0Hozp5zbExtYQqrH5Qwq4jSIUzXSCF3U-Gt2gOZQLgBabENZ3PlBF7NtI|dead-url=no}}</ref>都表示了不认可，而亚历山大牧首[[西奥多卢斯二世|西奥多卢斯二世]]此前已发表声明宣布不支持乌克兰教会的分裂。<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.rt.com/news/439942-ukraine-church-unity-theodore/|title=Patriarch of Alexandria pledges support to canonical Ukrainian Church, urges Orthodox unity (VIDEO)|author=|date=2018-09-29|work=RT|accessdate=2019-01-08|archive-date=2020-11-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201109021451/https://www.rt.com/news/439942-ukraine-church-unity-theodore/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

